  <tr>
    <td colspan="3" width="100%"><p align="center">
    <font color="#9f3215" face="verdana" size="2">Giant spiders are common in Norrath, and when first spotted by the amateur adventurer produce terror.  They are truly huge and equally impressive.  They usually have good loot for someone between levels 8-11.  Their poison is not incredibly deadly, although it will do a little extra hurt and prevent healing afterwards.</font></td>
